OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChronic fatigue guidelines 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fscrap exercise therapy     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fadvice                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A health watchdog has published a      
OL,6, long-awaited and contentious final     
OL,7, update to ME treatment guidance.       
OL,9,FThe National Institute of Health and   
OL,10,FCare Excellence (NICE) has scrapped a  
OL,11,Fprevious recommendation of graded      
OL,12,Fexercise therapy.                      
OL,14,FMany patients with ME or chronic       
OL,15,Ffatigue syndrome (CFS) say the therapy,
OL,16,Fwhich encourages patients to slowly    
OL,17,Fincrease their levels of activity,     
OL,18,Fmakes their condition worse.           
OL,20,FThe advice was due out in August.      
